At this point I've tried moving the colorizer to a downstream messaging queue (which is also threaded) and it also crashes. Basically anytime I call colorizer from a thread, the program crashes. If I keep in downstream (like right before rendering) everything seems to work fine. I really only need the colorized video frames from the depth data and after that I don't need depth data anymore. 

